snippet.title: SOULCALIBUR VI - PS4/XB1/PC - Libra of Soul Story Mode Gamescom Reveal
snippet.description:
What if your fate was entwined with the two swords? Become the hero of your own legend with Libra of Soul, the new story mode introduced in SOULCALIBUR VI. Take up your weapon and make history on October 19!
